data.description: Just Reduced! And Seller offering up to $5,000 towards Rate Buydown, Buyers Closing Costs, or Down Payment! Fun in the Sun in your own POOL!! With a large kitchen open to the family room; a bay window, jetted tub, and separate shower in the owners suite; this beautiful rambler is settled in the Heart of the amazing Coral Canyon. Half a block from the elementary school; near a golf course, shopping, dining, and hiking/mountain biking trails; and close to National Parks, it is conveniently located to all that St. George has to offer!
